[package]
name = "rust"
edition = "2021"
version = "0.0.1"
authors = ["Aditya Kristianto <kristianto.aditya@gmail.com>"]

[dependencies]
actix = "0.13.3"
actix-cors = "0.7.0"
actix-files = "0.6.5"
actix-governor = "0.5.0"
actix-http = "3.7.0"
actix-limitation = "0.5.1"
actix-multipart = "0.6.1"
actix-ratelimit = "0.3.1"
actix-rt = "2.9.0"
actix-service = "2.0.2"
actix-session = "0.9.0"
actix-swagger = "0.3.1"
actix-utils = "3.0.1"
actix-web = "4.6.0"
actix-web-actors = "4.3.1+deprecated"
actix-web-httpauth = "0.8.1"
askama = "0.12.1"
async-std = "1.12.0"
bson = "2.10.0"
bytes = "1.4"
calamine = "0.25.0"
chrono = "0.4.38"
dotenv = "0.15.0"
dotenv_codegen = "0.15.0"
env_logger = "0.11.5"
futures = "0.3.30"
futures-io = "0.3.30"
futures-util = "0.3.30"
html-escape = "0.2.13"
http = "1.1.0"
json = "0.12.4"
kafka = "0.10.0"
log = "0.4.21"
mime = "0.3.17"
mongodb = "2.8.2"
oauth2 = "4.4.2"
openapi = "0.1.5"
openssl = "0.10.64"
pin-utils = "0.1.0"
postgres-types = "0.2.6"
ppv-lite86 = "0.2.17"
rand = "0.8.5"
rand_chacha = "0.3.1"
redis = "0.25.4"
regex = "1.10.4"
reqwest = "0.12.4"
rust_decimal = "1.35.0"
scraper = "0.19.0"
serde_json = "1.0.117"
serde_yaml = "0.9.34"
signal-hook-registry = "1.4.2"
sqlx = "0.7.4"
swagger = "6.5.0"
tempfile = "3.10.1"
tera = "1.20.0"
tinyvec = "1.6.0"
tokio-postgres = "0.7.10"
url = "2.5.0"
validator = "0.18.1"
value-bag = "1.9.0"
waitgroup = "0.1.2"
warp = "0.3.7"
webp = "0.3.0"
wrap = "0.1.0"

[dependencies.cmake]
version = "0.1.50 "
optional = true

[dependencies.diesel]
version = "2.2.0"
features = ["postgres"]

[dependencies.postgres]
version = "0.19.7"
features = ["with-chrono-0_4", "with-uuid-1"]

[dependencies.rdkafka]
version = "0.36.2"
features = ["cmake-build"]

[dependencies.serde]
version = "1.0.203"
features = ["derive"]

[dependencies.tokio]
version = "1.38.0"
features = ["full"]

[dependencies.utoipa]
version = "4.2.3"
features = ["actix_extras", "openapi_extensions"]

[dependencies.utoipa-swagger-ui]
version = "7.1.0"
features = ["actix-web"]

[dependencies.uuid]
version = "1.2.2"
features = ["v4", "fast-rng", "macro-diagnostics"]

[target.'cfg(target_arch = "arm")'.dependencies]

[target.'cfg(target_arch = "arm")'.dev-dependencies]

[target.'cfg(target_arch = "arm")'.build-dependencies]

[lib]
path = "src/lib.rs"
name = "rust"
plugin = false
proc-macro = false
edition = "2021"
required-features = []
crate-type = ["rlib"]

[profile.release]
opt-level = "z"
lto = true
codegen-units = 1
panic = "abort"
incremental = true
strip = "debuginfo"

[profile.release.package]

[profile.dev]
opt-level = 0
debug = 0
incremental = true
strip = false

[profile.dev.package]
